reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I needed a small bookshelf for my largely academic collection of books that have spent the last year in boxes in the basement. My biggest concern was whether it would be able to hold the weight of my books, but the product description states that each shelf can hold up to 60 lbs, so I gave it a shot. Each box I had held about 1 shelf's worth of books, and each box weighed about 40 lbs. I've only had this for about 3 months, but the shelves are not showing any signs of bowing, so I'm cautiously optimistic that this bookshelf will hold up.The color was exactly what I was expecting, assembly was simple, and it is a sturdy bookcase.
